text: The South African Maintenance and Estate Beneficiaries Association (SAMEBA) is a South African political party. Their platform is made up of two main elements; child maintenance and beneficiaries of estates. The party contested the 2014 general election in Limpopo province and contested the 2019 general election, failing to win any seats. == Election results == ===National elections=== |- ! Election !
